 month grace period, and is renewable up to three years. All registered businesses benefit from the services and facilities below:</p>\r\n<p>Services:</p>\r\n<p>• Event/Exhibition Participation </p>\r\n<p>• BBIC active follow up on business progress</p>\r\n<p>• Advisory services BDB Group</p>\r\n<p>• Benefit from Tamkeen Subsidy</p>\r\n<p>• Facilitated access to a business loan from BDB</p>\r\n<p>• Weekly unit cleaning</p>\r\n<p>• Unit maintenance</p>\r\n<p>• Advertisement space on the BBIC website and on main building’s product showcase</p>\r\n<p>• Internet access.</p>\r\n<p>• Photocopying and faxing services.</p>\r\n<p>• Telephone answering services.</p>\r\n<p>• 24/7 secured gate access to the building and sites.</p>\r\n<p>Facilities:</p>\r\n<p>• Air Conditioned Offices</p>\r\n<p>• Business lounge</p>\r\n<p>• Smoking room</p>\r\n<p>• On-site parking for tenants and their clients</p>\r\n<p>• Shared and equipped boardroom/meeting room facilities</p>\r\n<p>• Shared and equipped seminar and conference rooms with access for up to 60 people.</p>\r\n<p>• Central area reception</p>\r\n<p>• Two Food Vendors on-site</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>To apply please submit the necessary documents found <a href=\"http://afternoon-falls-9745.herokuapp.com/bbic/joomla/index.php/en/downloads/office-application\">here</a> and arrange for a meeting or drop by the BBIC for document submission. To contact us please click <a href=\"http://afternoon-falls-9745.herokuapp.com/bbic/joomla/index.php/en/contactuscat\">here</a>.</p>','',1,43,'2014-09-27 20:28:13',669,'','2014-10-19 07:11:49',669,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2014-09-27 20:28:13','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"t