Solutions','ack-solutions','<h1 style=\"color: #0099ff; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 29px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; text-transform: uppercase;\">ARE YOU INTERESTED IN INCREASING SALES AND DEVELOPING A MARKETING STRATEGY FOR YOUR BUSINESS IN THE MIDDLE EAST?</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\"><b>ACK Solutions works with small and large organizations across the Middle East, helping them to develop their marketing strategy, which enables them to increase sales, attract and retain clients, and provide better products and services.</b> Whether your company is native to the region or you want to break into the lucrative Middle East market with a new product or service offering, we can help you.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #244c5e; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: -1px;\">How can a marketing strategy help your business grow?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\"><b>Marketing often gets overlooked in many companies. </b>Many organizations in the Middle East offer a great product or service, but don’t have a marketing strategy, or a way of communicating the value of what they sell to their market. They jump straight into advertising or PR without truly getting their marketing strategy right. This can lead to customers that are confused about what you actually sell, ineffective communication to the market, a lack of focus, and missed sales opportunities.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\"><b>Having a marketing strategy will position your company for success. </b>We are moving away from selling situations where the seller knows it all and the buyer is left without knowing much about what they are buying. In today’s uber-connected business world, your customers have unlimited access to information about what you sell, what your past customers like or dislike about your products, and can make informed choices without needing to directly communicate with you. Your customers are able to find out anything about the products or services they are looking to purchase by simply typing a few keywords into Google. What are you doing to make sure that they find you, understand you, and want to buy from you?</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\"><b>The key to increasing sales is not only about giving your customers what they want, but also in knowing how to communicate with them.</b> Sometimes this means starting at the very beginning by asking your target customers what they want, looking at what the competition is doing, and assessing where the opportunities are in the market. Other times it is just about determining the best way to effectively communicate about a great product that you already have and developing the channels to make it happen.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #244c5e; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: -1px;\">Whether you are a small business or a large corporation, knowing your market and how to communicate your value is the foundation of increasing your sales.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\"><b>ACK Solutions has extensive experience in marketing consulting in the Middle East. </b>We help companies to dramatically improve their marketing and sales results by offering