ign: justify;\\\" \\/><br style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\">The company\'s current business lines have been clearly distinguished to cover Electronic Prototyping , Control &amp; Automation and Software Development.<\\/span><br style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\" \\/><br style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\">With a 100% Bahranization employment rate , YNH is privileged to establish business contacts and undertake technical projects alongside numerous educational institutes and business orgnizations in addtion to access to most countries located regionally.<\\/span><br style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\" \\/><br style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"color: #666666; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\\\">As YNH pushes into new frontiers , it remains dedicated to its prime objectives of helping people improve their life quality through technology as well as supporting the GO Green perception.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":56,\"created\":\"2014-09-30 14:21:21\",\"created_by\":\"671\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-14 10