, promote a culture of learning and further the cause of the industry as a whole.Ultimately we hope to make it an exciting option for young graduates looking for new career paths- through workshops, seminars, training programmes, conferences and other on-going tools to assist individuals and corporations to \\\"dive within their psyches and discover the perls within\\\".<\\/b><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h2>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":63,\"created\":\"2014-09-30 14:19:47\",\"created_by\":\"671\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-14 10:59:53\",\"modified_by\":\"670\",\"checked_out\":\"670\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2014-10-14 10:59:44\",\"publish_up\":\"2014-09-30 14:19:47\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"\",\"urls\":\"\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"companyprofile_address1\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"companyprofile_address2\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"companyprofile_block\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"companyprofile_area\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"companyprofile_pobox\\\":\\\"75798\\\",\\\"companyprofile_tel\\\":\\\"17300547\\\",\\\"companyprofile_website\\\":\\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/www.takatofbh.com\\\\\\/\\\",\\\"companyprofile_logo\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/company_logos\\\\\\/takatof.png\\\",\\\"companyprofile_category\\\":\\\"5\\\",\\\"companyprofile_language\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"companyprofile_approval\\\":\\\"1\\\"}\",\"version\":3,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"2\",\"metadata\":\"\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0),(683,212,1,'','2014-10-14 11:00:18',670,2321,'f9a36510ed8bf45b874036905134267da8f1b15c','{\"id\":212,\"asset_id\":\"393\",\"title\":\"Jeeves\",\"alias\":\"jeeves\",\"introtext\":\"<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.4em; font-size: 1.1em; text-align: justify; font-family: \'Gill Sans MT\', \'Gill Sans\', Verdanda, sans-serif;\\\">Carrying on a most venerable tradition, Jeeves offers gentlemen and ladies an unmatched personal valeting service. With almost 40 years\\u2019 experience, Jeeves has developed the skill required to ensure the safe cleaning and maintenance of your entire wardrobe. Truly, quality garments, fabrics and accessories deserve the attention of none other.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.4em; font-size: 1.1em; text-align: justify; font-family: \'Gill Sans MT\', \'Gill Sans\', Verdanda, sans-serif;\\\">First established among London\'s Belgravia grand terraces in 1969, Jeeves is today the garment care specialist of choice for a discerning international clientele that includes royalty, haute couture houses and stylish individuals like you.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 1.4em; font-size: 1.1em; text-align: justify; font-family: \'Gill Sans MT\', \'Gill Sans\', Verdanda, sans-serif;\\\">Now serving\\u00a0Bahrain\\u00a0with\\u00a0an elegant shop, a FREE\\u00a0collection and delivery service, as ever, Jeeves is at your service.\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":62,\"created\":\"2014-09-30 14:16:08\",\"created_by\":\"671\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-14 11:00:18\",\"modified_by\":\"670\",\"checked_out\":\"670\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2014-10-14 11:00:08\",\"publish_up\":\"2014-09-30 14:16:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"\",\"urls\":\"\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"companyprofile_address1\\\":\\\"Units 132 & 134, Bahrain Business Incubator Centre,\\\",\\\"companyprofile_address2\\\":\\\"Dry Dock Road 1727,\\\",\\\"companyprofile_block\\\":\\\"117\\\",\\\"companyprofile_area\\\":\\\"Hidd\\\",\\\"companyprofile_pobox\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"companyprofile_tel\\\":\\\"17465575\\\",\\\"companyprofile_website\\\":\\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/www.jeevesbahrain.com\\\\\\/\\\",\\\"companyprofile_logo\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/company_logos\\\\\\/jeeves.jpg\\\",\\\"companyprofile_category\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"companyprofile_language\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"companyprofile_approval\\\":\\\"1\\\"}\",\"version\":4,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"2\",\"metadata\":\"\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0),(684,210,1,'','2014-10-14 11:00:35',670,7450,'ac4e779706434a9fc913d82fd417625269a1b321','{\"id\":210,\"asset_id\":\"391\",\"title\":\"ACK Solutions\",\"alias\":\"ack-solutions\",\"introtext\":\"<h1 style=\\\"color: #0099ff; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 29px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: normal; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; text-transform: uppercase;\\\">ARE YOU INTERESTED IN INCREASING SALES AND DEVELOPING A MARKETING STRATEGY FOR YOUR BUSINESS IN THE MIDDLE EAST?<\\/h1>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\\\"><b>ACK Solutions works with small and large organizations across the Middle East, helping them to develop their marketing strategy, which enables them to increase sales, attract and retain clients, and provide better products and services.<\\/b>\\u00a0Whether your company is native to the region\\u00a0or you want to break into the\\u00a0lucrative Middle East market with a new product or service offering, we can help you.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #244c5e; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: -1px;\\\">How can a marketing strategy help your business grow?<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\\\"><b>Marketing often gets overlooked in many companies.\\u00a0<\\/b>Many organizations in the Middle East offer a great product or service, but don\\u2019t have a marketing strategy, or a way of communicating the value of what they sell to their market. They jump straight into advertising or PR without truly getting their marketing strategy right. This can lead to customers that are confused about what you actually sell, ineffective communication to the market, a lack of focus, and missed sales opportunities.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\\\"><b>Having a marketing strategy will position your company for success.\\u00a0<\\/b>We are moving away from selling situations where the seller knows it all and the buyer is left without knowing much about what they are buying. In today\\u2019s uber-connected business world, your customers have unlimited access to information about what you sell, what your past customers like or dislike about your products, and can make informed choices without needing to directly communicate with you. Your customers are able to find out anything about the products or services they are looking to purchase by simply typing a few keywords into Google. What are you doing to make sure that they find you, understand you, and want to buy from you?<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\\\"><b>The key to increasing sales is not only about giving your customers what they want, but also in knowing how to communicate with them.<\\/b>\\u00a0Sometimes this means starting at the very beginning by asking your target customers what they want, looking at what the competition is doing, and assessing where the opportunities are in the market. Other times it is just about determining the best way to effectively communicate about a great product that you already have and developing the channels to make it happen.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #244c5e; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: -1px;\\\">Whether you are a small business or a large corporation, knowing your market and how to communicate your value is the foundation of increasing your sales.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\\\"><b>ACK Solutions has extensive experience in marketing consulting in the Middle East.\\u00a0<\\/b>We\\u00a0help companies to dramatically improve their marketing and sales results by offering more effective ways of attracting customers and significantly better products and services.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #244c5e; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: -1px;\\\">Start by downloading our\\u00a0<a style=\\\"color: #244c5e; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px;\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/acksolutions.com\\/thought-leadership\\/free-report\\/\\\">marketing plan template<\\/a>, or by sending us a message to get started on your marketing strategy today!<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #444444; font-weight: bold;\\\">Please take the time to review our widely-read marketing and sales blog, which includes regular insights, tips, and strategies on various marketing and sales related issues facing companies in the Middle East.<\\/span>\\u00a0The best way to start is by downloading our free marketing plan template on the left had side of this screen. You can also see a sample video of our Marketing Insider online marketing course, which will show you step by step how to increase sales, attract more clients and customers, and make more money. Finally, you can send us a message to get started on improving your marketing strategy today!<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #244c5e; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: -1px;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/h2>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #244c5e; font-family: spinnakerregular, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-shadow: white 0px 1px 1px; letter-spacing: -1px;\\\">Where To Next?<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 23.4375px; margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px;\\\">Now you have an overview of our company. To learn the details of who we work with, the problems we solve for them, and the characteristics of our most successful clients, click on the link to see\\u00a0<a style=\\\"color: #00aeef;\\\" title=\\\"Who We Work With\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/acksolutions.com\\/?page_id=6\\\">Who We Work With<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":49,\"created\":\"2014-09-30 13:10:23\",\"created_by\":\"671\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-14 11:00:35\",\"modified_by\":\"670\",\"checked_out\":\"670\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2014-10-14 11:00:28\",\"publish_up\":\"2014-09-30 13:10:23\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"\",\"urls\":\"\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"companyprofile_address1\\\":\\\"Suite 4102 \\\\u2013 Tower AA1\\\",\\\"companyprofile_address2\\\":\\\"Mazaya Business Avenue\\\",\\\"companyprofile_block\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"companyprofile_area\\\":\\\"Jumeriah Lakes Towers, Dubai,\\\",\\\"companyprofile_pobox\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"companyprofile_tel\\\":\\\"971503164956\\\",\\\"companyprofile_website\\\":\\\"http:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/acksolutions.com\\\\\\/\\\",\\\"companyprofile_logo\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/company_logos\\\\\\/acksolutions.png\\\",\\\"companyprofile_category\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"companyprofile_language\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"companyprofile_approval\\\":\\\"1\\\"}\",\"version\":4,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\"