\" \\/><param name=\\\"allowscriptaccess\\\" value=\\\"always\\\" \\/><embed src=\\\"\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/v\\/pI5lTbC9Dkg?version=3&amp;hl=en_US&amp;rel=0\\\" type=\\\"application\\/x-shockwave-flash\\\" width=\\\"560\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" \\/><\\/object><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">Our Mission<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\">Our mission is to\\u00a0 facilitate the establishment and growth of start-up business in the Kingdom of Bahrain.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">Our Vision<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\">Our vision is to encourage the expansion of an enterprising, entreprenureal, and innovative culture in the Kingdom of Bahrain.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: normal;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The Bahrain Business Incubator Centre (BBIC) was established in 2003 as the first mixed-use incubation\\u00a0center in the G.C.C. The Center\\u2019s mission since its establishment is to support the growth and sustainability of small and medium enterprises (SME\\u2019s) in Bahrain. The BBIC is achieving this mission by\\u00a0providing governmentally approved physical spaces for business to start and grow, receiving tailored\\u00a0facilities and services designed to increase the success rate and sustainability of our tenants.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Bahrain Development Bank (BDB), the leading SME funding of the Kingdom of Bahrain, established the\\u00a0BBIC as a means to aid in the economic development of the country, through providing a full scope\\u00a0incubation program, to aid the growth of startup businesses. The BBIC remains a fully owned and\\u00a0pioneering subsidiary of the BDB, which is expanding and growing in a sustainable manner.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our growth was possible through the support of all our affiliates, both nationally and internationally.\\u00a0The support we have received through our government, from support institutions such as Tamkeen, has\\u00a0enabled us to progress and accelerate the growth of our tenants along with our organization.\\u00a0The BBIC has graduated over 100+ businesses into the market successfully, since its inception and is\\u00a0looking to graduate a lot more in the coming years.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"30\",\"created\":\"2014-09-08 14:09:14\",\"created_by\":\"669\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2014-10-19 07:16:29\",\"modified_by\":\"669\",\"checked_out\":\"669\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2014-10-19